author: mukulg
msg: committing few improvements related to processing of QName lists (the QName strings must be in correct lexical form, and the prefixes must be declared in the schema) involved in conditional inclusion namespace (vc:).
This improvement passes few additional tests specified in W3C XML Schema 1.1 test suite (specifically vc904.xsd & vc905.xsd).
The commit also includes few minor javadoc improvements.
